    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exosuit Appearance Override</span>.<br><br>Hardened against the extreme conditions found beneath the waves, this jetpack replacement allows for smooth and stylish passage through the murky abyss.<br><br>Transform the appearance of your Exosuit at an <span class=\"name name-technology\">Appearance Modifier</span>.",
